snippet.textDisplay: What a pity this hadith sharif " man kuntomaula fa haza Ali maula" had to be put into music hundreds of years ago to make it easy for Muslims to digest. Ali is the Oolul Ilm and spiritual successor of the Holy Prophet's spiritual legacy. You can not have Ishq for Allah and His holy Prophet without first learning how to love at the feet of  Master of Spiritual Awareness- Maula Ali. This is what the Holy Prophet has ordered us to do in this hadith sharif: to seek spiritual consciousness from Ali after the demise of the Holy Prophet. Music becomes purified by taking his name-- which is Allah's Ism-e- Husna as well, because Ali symbolizes the Forces of Truth revealed by Allah to the world. One can not ask for true spiritual consciousness without love for and obedience to Ali--this is the meaning when we ask for his 'help'--he helps us to take the direct path to Allah.
